  "merge_notes": "School conflict: 'General' (1 card) vs 'ICT' (1 card); picked ICT by majority. The 'Daily Profiles' card focuses on pre-CPI indecision, while 'Education - ICT' focuses on post-CPI SMT setups; both perspectives preserved.",
